\begin_layout Section
The command line: 
\emph on
tidy.source()
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The main function is 
\emph on
tidy.source()
\emph default
, which can take a file as input, parse it and write the formatted code
 to the console or a file.
 
\end_layout

